name: DP PARTNERS PJP-I, LP, Petitioner v. COURT OF COMMON PLEAS OF PHILADELPHIA COUNTY, Respondent
name_abbreviation: DP Partners PJP-I, LP v. Court of Common Pleas

parties: DP PARTNERS PJP-I, LP, Petitioner v. COURT OF COMMON PLEAS OF PHILADELPHIA COUNTY, Respondent.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 15th day of October, 2012, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the “Petition of DP Partners Requesting that this Court Exercise Plenary Jurisdiction and for a Writ of Prohibition” is DENIED.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
